## Tool-Specific Notes

### Web Search (Research)
- **Use for:** Prospect company research, industry analysis, competitive intelligence
- **Best practices:** Verify information accuracy, check recency, cross-reference sources

### Agentmail (Email)
- **Use for:** Cold outreach, follow-ups, proposal delivery, relationship nurturing
- **Best practices:** Personalize messages, follow up appropriately, respect opt-outs

### Slack (Communication)
- **Use for:** Team coordination, deal updates, escalation requests
- **Best practices:** Keep channels organized, tag appropriately, respect urgency levels

